Patch Set 1:

To difficult to add unit test for this scenario as not able to set value of 'os_glance_staging_store' using self.config method as well as not able to mock it. I can add functional test to verify that if image is deleted after staging call (before import call) then data can be deleted from staging store. Since image is so small in functional tests it is also difficult to verify that if image is deleted during import call staging data is cleared.
